    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You’ve been trained to operate firearms and ship’s cannons. You gain access to all uncommon firearms. You have familiarity with firearms and siege equipment - for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons. Additionally, you treat this calculated proficiency as your class DC proficiency for the usage of siege engines.</p><p>At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p>",
